Text: West Point Inn December th Cc Everyone I reserved the West Point Inn for a December th get together It should be a good time for sitting by the fire drinking egg nog and white russians and hanging out with friends I hope you all can make it Please let me know Also let me know if you want to invite any friends WPIkdoc Sean WPIkdoc
